  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of this clinical trial is to assess the long-term safety and efficacy of GS010, a
      gene therapy, and assess the quality of life in subjects with LHON due to the G11778A ND4
      mitochondrial mutation and who were treated in the Rescue or Reverse studies.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
