    <description>Change of GCL thickness/volume and topographical map and other parameters measured by SD-OCT using a mixed model of ANCOVA</description>
  </secondary_outcome>
  <secondary_outcome>
    <measure>Quality of Life: Visual Functioning Questionnaire 25 (VFQ-25)</measure>
